      right: ["Severe hypertension ≥160/110 mmHg unresponsive to treatment","Eclamptic seizure (tonic-clonic activity)","Absent deep tendon reflexes with respiratory depression (Mg toxicity)","HELLP syndrome: hemolysis, elevated liver enzymes, low platelets","Pulmonary edema with oxygen desaturation","Placental abruption with vaginal bleeding and uterine rigidity"]
