    pearls: ["Magnesium sulfate is the GOLD STANDARD for eclampsia seizure prophylaxis -- it is NOT primarily an antihypertensive","The three essential assessments before each magnesium dose: respiratory rate ≥12, DTRs present, urine output ≥30 mL/hr","Calcium gluconate 1 g IV over 3-5 minutes is the antidote for magnesium toxicity -- keep at bedside at all times","HELLP syndrome = Hemolysis (elevated LDH, schistocytes), Elevated Liver enzymes, Low Platelets -- a life-threatening variant of severe preeclampsia","The only definitive treatment for preeclampsia is DELIVERY of the placenta -- all other treatments are temporizing measures","Eclampsia can occur antepartum, intrapartum, or up to 6 weeks postpartum -- continue monitoring after delivery","Preeclampsia with severe features at ≥34 weeks: delivery is recommended; at <34 weeks: consider expectant management with steroids for lung maturity"],
